lines.text:
[shaking his glove that he mistakes for the frog that swallowed Wilbur]
Cough up Wilbur! Cough him up!
[Goofy has tried but failed to get at the stork that swallowed the frog that had swallowed Wilbur]
I gotta cheer up. There's lots of grasshoppers in the weeds.
[suddenly, an egg hatches revealing Wilbur, very much alive]
Wilbur! Gosh, Wilbur, thought you was a goner.
